Body:
assert 1 + 2 + 3 + 4 == execute('add: 1, 2, 3 and 4')
assert 55.3 + 6 + 3 == execute('sum of 55.3, 6, 3')
assert -10 + 5 == execute('calculate the sum of -10 and 5')
assert 10000300 + 20.3 == execute('add 10,000,300 and 20.3')
assert 10000000 + 300 + 20.3 == execute('add 10,000,000, 300, and 20.3')
assert 10000000 + 300 + 20.3 == execute('10,000,000 + 300+20.3')
assert 100000 + 300 + 20.3 == execute('add 1e5, 300, and 20.3')
